    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510540/extras/b9de46abf4f498d66ce42c11799898e6.poster.avif?t=1764629097\" width=610 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510540/extras/b9de46abf4f498d66ce42c11799898e6.webm?t=1764629097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510540/extras/b9de46abf4f498d66ce42c11799898e6.mp4?t=1764629097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Long Gone Days》是一款以现实世界为背景的角色扮演游戏，讲述了战争期间人与人之间的情感联系，重点聚焦于平民生活、语言隔阂以及国界问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将跟随罗克的脚步，这位从小就被训练成狙击手的年轻人，他效忠于一个名为“核心”的地下准军事组织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在他的首次任务中，他肩负着一项极其重要的命令被派往了地面。他满怀期待，终于有机会展示自己多年训练的成果。他完美地执行了第一个命令，然而却意外地发现，核心组织远非他心中所想的那般崇高与正义。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510540/extras/7c69c11f04db6a59500a9c81776243eb.poster.avif?t=1764629097\" width=614 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510540/extras/7c69c11f04db6a59500a9c81776243eb.webm?t=1764629097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510540/extras/7c69c11f04db6a59500a9c81776243eb.mp4?t=1764629097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战争的多维度视角体验：通过激烈的角色扮演战斗与平和的生活片段式玩法的鲜明对比，你将亲身体验到现代冲突与平民生活之间的强烈反差。</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沟通至关重要：《Long Gone Days》以现实世界为背景，你将遇到多种语言障碍。记得招募翻译官来帮忙沟通，以便跨越国界建立深厚联系。</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保持士气高昂：明智地选择对话选项以在战斗中提振士气。每个角色都拥有独特的性格特征和动机。</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狙击模式：《Long Gone Days》设有两种战斗系统。你可以使用罗克的步枪，瞄准敌人并将其一举击毙。。</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无随机遭遇战：《Long Gone Days》采用正面视角和回合制战斗系统，设有身体部位瞄准机制。每一场战斗都经过精心设计，与剧情直接相关。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
